WEBVTT

00:02:28.231 --> 00:02:32.082
because it's an easy way to not
think about your own issues.

00:02:32.106 --> 00:02:33.384
Isn't it?

00:02:33.408 --> 00:02:34.888
Hmm? Hmm? Hmm?

00:02:34.912 --> 00:02:37.174
(Laughter)

00:02:37.198 --> 00:02:38.348
OK.

00:02:39.428 --> 00:02:42.213
The turning point came

00:02:42.237 --> 00:02:47.343
when I fell into an emotionally
abusive relationship

00:02:47.367 --> 00:02:48.891
just a few years ago.

00:02:49.492 --> 00:02:51.713
He isolated me

00:02:51.737 --> 00:02:55.370
and left me feeling more alone than ever.

00:02:56.565 --> 00:02:58.347
It was the lowest point in my life,

00:02:58.371 --> 00:03:01.451
but it was also my wake-up call,